items.headline: Welcome to The Killing Wikia
items.desc: The Killing Wikia is a community site dedicated to the AMC TV series The Killing. If you are a fan of this series, or even if you're just curious about it, then this is the place for you! Come explore our content and help us expand this database... or join us in discussion about the characters, the episodes, or the series in general. All are welcome!
